trans-unit.source: Returns the green color component for the specified pixel, scaled from 0 to 255 in the default RGB ColorSpace, sRGB. A color conversion is done if necessary. The pixel value is specified by an array of data elements of type transferType passed in as an object reference. The returned value is a non pre-multiplied value. Thus, if the alpha is premultiplied, this method divides it out before returning the value. If the alpha value is 0, for example, the green value is 0. If inData is not a primitive array of type transferType, a ClassCastException is thrown. An ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException is thrown if inData is not large enough to hold a pixel value for this ColorModel. The visual presentation of the columns is the responsibility of the view/controller object using this model (typically JTable). Because the model does not know how the columns are laid out on screen, the given xPosition should not be considered to be a coordinate in 2D graphics space. trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the last occurrence of the specified element in this list, or -1 if this list does not contain the element.
trans-unit.target: 返回指定元素在列表中最后出现的索引,如果列表中不包含该元素,则返回-1。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the last occurrence of the specified element in this list, or -1 if this list does not contain the element. More formally, returns the highest index i such that (o==null ? get(i)==null : o.equals(get(i))), or -1 if there is no such index.
trans-unit.target: 返回指定元素在此列表中最后一次出现的索引；如果此列表不包含该元素，则返回-1。更正式地，返回最高索引 i ，使 (o==null ? get(i)==null : o.equals(get(i))) ；如果没有这样的索引，则返回-1。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the last occurrence of the specified element in this list, or -1 if this list does not contain the element. More formally, returns the highest index i such that Objects.equals(o, get(i)), or -1 if there is no such index.
trans-unit.target: 返回指定元素在此列表中最后一次出现的索引；如果此列表不包含该元素，则返回-1。更正式地，返回最高索引 i ,这样 Objects.equals(o, get(i)) 或-1（如果没有这样的索引）。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the last occurrence of the specified element in this list, searching backwards from index, or returns -1 if the element is not found.
trans-unit.target: 返回此列表中指定元素最后一次出现的 index ，从index向后搜索，如果未找到该元素，则返回-1。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the last occurrence of the specified element in this list, searching backwards from index, or returns -1 if the element is not found. More formally, returns the highest index i such that (i <= index && (e==null ? get(i)==null : e.equals(get(i)))), or -1 if there is no such index.
trans-unit.target: 返回此列表中指定元素最后一次出现的 index ，从index向后搜索，如果未找到该元素，则返回-1。更正式地，返回最高索引 i ，使得 (i <= index && (e==null ? get(i)==null : e.equals(get(i)))) ；如果没有这样的索引，则返回-1指数。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the last occurrence of the specified element in this list, searching backwards from index, or returns -1 if the element is not found. More formally, returns the highest index i such that i <= index && Objects.equals(get(i), e), or -1 if there is no such index.
trans-unit.target: 返回此列表中指定元素最后一次出现的 index ，从index向后搜索，如果未找到该元素，则返回-1。更正式地，返回最高索引 i ，以使 i <= index && Objects.equals(get(i), e) ；如果没有这样的索引，则返回-1。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the nearest bit that is set to false that occurs on or before the specified starting index.
trans-unit.target: 返回在指定的起始索引上或之前出现的，设置为 false 的最近位的索引。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the nearest bit that is set to false that occurs on or before the specified starting index. If no such bit exists, or if -1 is given as the starting index, then -1 is returned.
trans-unit.target: 返回在指定的起始索引上或之前出现的，设置为 false 的最近位的索引。如果不存在这样的位，或者如果将 -1 作为起始索引，则返回 -1 。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the nearest bit that is set to true that occurs on or before the specified starting index.
trans-unit.target: 返回在指定的起始索引上或之前出现的，设置为 true 的最近位的索引。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the nearest bit that is set to true that occurs on or before the specified starting index. If no such bit exists, or if -1 is given as the starting index, then -1 is returned.
trans-unit.target: 返回在指定的起始索引上或之前出现的，设置为 true 的最近位的索引。如果不存在这样的位，或者如果将 -1 作为起始索引，则返回 -1 。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the rightmost (lowest-order) one bit in this BigInteger (the number of zero bits to the right of the rightmost one bit).
trans-unit.target: 返回这个BigInteger中最右边(最低阶)一位的索引(最右边一位右边的零位数)。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the rightmost (lowest-order) one bit in this BigInteger (the number of zero bits to the right of the rightmost one bit). Returns -1 if this BigInteger contains no one bits. (Computes (this == 0? -1 : log2(this & -this)).)
trans-unit.target: 返回此BigInteger中最右边（最低位）的一位的索引（最右边一位的右边的零位数）。如果此BigInteger不包含任何位，则返回-1。（计算 (this == 0? -1 : log2(this & -this)) 。）

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the row that point lies in, or -1 if the result is not in the range [0, getRowCount()-1].
trans-unit.target: 返回该 point 所在行的索引；如果结果不在[0， getRowCount() - 1]范围内，则返回-1。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the row that contains the cell currently being edited.

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the specified Component.
trans-unit.target: 返回指定组件的索引。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the specified Component. This is the absolute index, ignoring layers. Index numbers, like position numbers, have the topmost component at index zero. Larger numbers are closer to the bottom.
trans-unit.target: 返回指定组件的索引。这是绝对索引,忽略图层。索引号和位置号一样,最上面的组件的索引为零。数字越大,越接近底部。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the specified child in this node's child array.
trans-unit.target: 返回此节点的子数组中指定子节点的索引。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the specified child in this node's child array. If the specified node is not a child of this node, returns -1. This method performs a linear search and is O(n) where n is the number of children.
trans-unit.target: 返回此节点的子数组中指定子项的索引。如果指定的节点不是该节点的子节点，则返回 -1 。此方法执行线性搜索，并且为O（n），其中n是子代数。

trans-unit.target: 返回此网络接口的索引。索引是一个大于或等于零的整数，如果未知，则为 -1 。这是系统特定的值，并且具有相同名称的接口在不同的计算机上可以具有不同的索引。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index to the code array of the Code attribute containing the execution point represented by this stack frame.
trans-unit.target: 返回包含此堆栈框架表示的执行点的 Code 属性的代码数组的索引。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index where dropped data should be inserted into the associated component.
trans-unit.target: 返回应将放弃的数据插入到相关组件中的索引。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index where dropped data should be inserted into the associated component. This index represents a position between characters, as would be interpreted by a caret.
trans-unit.target: 返回应将丢弃的数据插入到相关组件中的索引。这个索引代表了字符之间的位置,就像卡口一样。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index where dropped data should be placed in the list.
trans-unit.target: 返回丢弃的数据应该放在列表中的索引。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index where dropped data should be placed in the list. Interpretation of the value depends on the drop mode set on the associated component. If the drop mode is either DropMode.USE_SELECTION or DropMode.ON, the return value is an index of a row in the list. If the drop mode is DropMode.INSERT, the return value refers to the index where the data should be inserted. If the drop mode is DropMode.ON_OR_INSERT, the value of isInsert() indicates whether the index is an index of a row, or an insert index.
trans-unit.target: 返回应该在列表中放置数据的索引。值的解释取决于在关联组件上设置的放置模式。如果放置模式是 DropMode.USE_SELECTION 或 DropMode.ON ，则返回值是列表中行的索引。如果放置模式为 DropMode.INSERT ，则返回值引用应在其中插入数据的索引。如果放置模式为 DropMode.ON_OR_INSERT ，则 isInsert() 的值指示索引是行索引还是插入索引。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index where the dropped data should be inserted with respect to the path returned by getPath().

The order of strings within the returned array is not defined.

trans-unit.source: Returns the list of known AttachingConnector objects.
trans-unit.target: 返回已知 AttachingConnector 对象的列表。

trans-unit.source: Returns the list of known AttachingConnector objects. Any of the returned objects can be used to attach to an existing target VM and create a VirtualMachine mirror for it.
trans-unit.target: 返回已知 AttachingConnector 对象的列表。返回的任何对象均可用于附加到现有目标VM并为其创建 VirtualMachine 镜像。

trans-unit.source: Returns the list of known LaunchingConnector objects.
trans-unit.target: 返回已知的 LaunchingConnector 对象的列表。

trans-unit.source: Returns the list of known LaunchingConnector objects. Any of the returned objects can be used to launch a new target VM and immediately create a VirtualMachine mirror for it. Note that a target VM launched by a launching connector is not guaranteed to be stable until after the VMStartEvent has been received.
trans-unit.target: 返回已知的 LaunchingConnector 对象的列表。返回的任何对象均可用于启动新的目标VM，并立即为其创建 VirtualMachine 镜像。请注意，只有在收到 VMStartEvent 之后，才能保证由启动连接器启动的目标VM是稳定的。

trans-unit.source: Returns the list of known ListeningConnector objects.
trans-unit.target: 返回已知的 ListeningConnector 对象的列表。

trans-unit.source: Returns the list of known ListeningConnector objects. Any of the returned objects can be used to listen for a connection initiated by a target VM and create a VirtualMachine mirror for it.
trans-unit.target: 返回已知的 ListeningConnector 对象的列表。任何返回的对象都可用于侦听目标VM发起的连接并为其创建 VirtualMachine 镜像。

trans-unit.target: 返回可用于标识该选项的名称列表。例如，选项“ -classpath”的列表可以是 ["-classpath", "--class-path"] ，别名为“ --class-path”。

trans-unit.source: Returns the list of operations of the MBean. Each operation is described by an MBeanOperationInfo object. The returned array is a shallow copy of the internal array, which means that it is a copy of the internal array of references to the MBeanOperationInfo objects but that each referenced MBeanOperationInfo object is not copied.
trans-unit.target: 返回MBean的操作列表。每个操作均由 MBeanOperationInfo 对象描述。返回的数组是内部数组的浅表副本，这意味着它是对 MBeanOperationInfo 对象的引用的内部数组的副本，但是未复制每个引用的 MBeanOperationInfo 对象。

trans-unit.source: Returns the list of platform MXBeans implementing the given mxbeanInterface in the Java virtual machine.

trans-unit.source: Returns the list of platform MXBeans implementing the given mxbeanInterface in the Java virtual machine. The returned list may contain zero, one, or more instances. The number of instances in the returned list is defined in the specification of the given management interface. The order is undefined and there is no guarantee that the list returned is in the same order as previous invocations.
trans-unit.target: 返回在Java虚拟机中实现给定 mxbeanInterface 的平台MXBean的列表。返回的列表可能包含零个，一个或多个实例。返回列表中实例的数量在给定管理接口的规范中定义。该顺序是不确定的，并且不能保证返回的列表与先前的调用顺序相同。

trans-unit.source: Returns the list of predefined configurations for this Java Virtual Machine (JVM).
trans-unit.target: 返回此Java虚拟机(JVM)的预定义配置列表。

trans-unit.source: Returns the list of role definitions (ArrayList of RoleInfo objects).
trans-unit.target: 返回角色定义的列表(RoleInfo对象的ArrayList)。

The returned list will contain a ReferenceType for each class or interface found with the given name. The search is confined to loaded classes only; no attempt is made to load a class of the given name.
trans-unit.target: 返回与给定名称匹配的已加载引用类型。该名称必须是完全限定的（例如，java.lang.String）。返回的列表将为使用给定名称找到的每个类或接口包含一个 ReferenceType 。搜索仅限于已加载的类；不会尝试加载给定名称的类。
